description: Backup file created by SurfSaver, a program that saves Web pages as users surf the Internet; contains a backup of an .ASK database file; created when askSam converts an older file to a new format so that the AS4 file may be opened by older software versions.

content: NOTE: AS4 files may safely be deleted if users do not intend to use older versions of askSam software.
